{"tid":2300812,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"日日翻工都一堆廢老係地鐵站排隊等免費報紙","createTime":"2020-11-25T23:45:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-26T00:32:39.000Z","uid":265521,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"679082c3e55eae9508b2e5f6d55c3a3e0281049d","tid":2300812,"uid":265521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T23:45:34.000Z","msg":"其實啲廢老日日排隊攞幾份免費報紙有咩意思?<br />\n首先，攞兩份報紙其實一樣，隨時佢未必識字<br />\n仲有幾乎兩日唔埋就會有廢老同派報紙員嘈交，開口埋口就人生攻擊，話人地啊姐係雞之類。"},{"pid":"d6bc53f6379424c11b07030d34b6df61d1c3115c","tid":2300812,"uid":78243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T23:52:26.000Z","msg":"攞去賣"},{"pid":"c443db4dc36e39cb7a09504bf778d228aa7a5db3","tid":2300812,"uid":65091,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T23:52:32.000Z","msg":"屌你真係戇鳩鳩咁<br />\n係咪一出世到而加未出過街<br />\n好明顯班廢老係拎去連埋d紙皮出去賣啦"},{"pid":"4f623936fcddd50d7f92646d56501eaedef69be1","tid":2300812,"uid":4285,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T23:55:52.000Z","msg":"對知識嘅渴求"},{"pid":"c2855bc50c61d2fbf0e05675c32c6a9eb107790b","tid":2300812,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T23:56:37.000Z","msg":"外判排隊拎報紙<br />\n<br />\n判上判"},{"pid":"67258e0449b856c380b5c3400bfd12cffc033d82","tid":2300812,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T23:58:49.000Z","msg":"係為啲 coupon<br />\n為啲紙就一定架啦<br />\n啲死廢老有舖唔執輸既癮<br />\n人拎佢拎"},{"pid":"f418dcb17386d00dd2ac8b316eb20c54fb0a7d9e","tid":2300812,"uid":33077,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T00:00:35.000Z","msg":"拎去賣 唔會幫佢<br />\n有個阿婆好興向閘外叫人幫佢拎<br />\n好仆街<br />\n人地有資訊俾人睇 唔係廢紙"},{"pid":"e0b92743941ba38aa0a1970f23a8386f7e6a8ea4","tid":2300812,"uid":37461,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T00:02:16.000Z","msg":"廢老太多時間，攞報紙已成為生存寄托<br />\n但係開口埋口叫人雞呢<br />\n相信呢個世上只有連登仔會咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43d5b683756